  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large pot over medium heat until shimmering.",
    "Add sliced onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in minced garlic and cook for 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Add diced tofu, carrots, and celery; sauté until veggies soften, about 5 minutes.",
    "Whisk tomato paste, red wine vinegar, oregano, thyme, and vegetable broth together.",
    "Temper the vinegar by whisking it with a small amount of hot oil before adding to the pot.",
    "Pour the mixture into the pot, bring to a gentle simmer, and cook for 20 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and pepper, then transfer to an agave leaf for serving."
